Now let's understand `GetColumnStyle` more carefully. In `XSSFSheet`:

```csharp
public ICellStyle GetColumnStyle(int column)
{
    EnsureWorksheetLoaded();
    IColumn col = GetColumn(column);
    if(col != null)
